<template><p>记录一些关于echart的属性及用法</p>
<h1 id="_1、title-主副标题" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1、title-主副标题" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <strong>1、title  主副标题</strong></h1>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token literal-property property">title</span> <span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
